(ghaybah): 
1. the daily prayers; 
2. the prayer of signs (ṣalāt al‑āyāt); 
3. the funeral prayer (ṣalāt al‑mayyit); 
4. the prayer for the obligatory circumambulation (ṭawāf) of the Kaʿbah; 
